These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, havana, siglo
3 different pets are kept: rat, mouse, goldfish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, water-polo, tennis
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, security-guard, fisherman
1. the manager is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the swisher-smoker is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the goldfish##2
4. the manager is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Cigar         | havana | swisher   | siglo   |
| Pet   | mouse     | rat | goldfish |
| Sport   | tennis  | surfing    | water-polo      |
| Job     | security-guard     | manager      | fisherman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
3 different games are played: chess, snooker, backgammon
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, water, lemonade
City: berlin, hannover, paris
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, zombie, satire
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person playing snooker is the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person playing chess is the person traveling to hannover##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is between the person drinking water and the person playing backgammon##2
6. the person playing backgammon is the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Game          | snooker  | chess     | backgammon     |
| Beverage   | water     | lemonade     | tea      |
| City   | paris  | hannover | berlin |
| Movie-Genre           | satire | adventure     | zombie       |

