.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, taxi, roller
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, light-blue, chestnut
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, blues, gospel
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, october, june
1. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the fan gospel##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who likes chestnut and the fan gospel##2
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is the person driving the taxi##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is the fan blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Transport          | scooter  | roller     | taxi     |
| Color           | chestnut | emerald  | light-blue   |
| Music-Genre   | house  | blues    | gospel |
| Birthday           | june     | july | october |

