.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, spanish, australian
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, comedy, spy
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, siglo, blend
3 different games are played: poker, whist, backgammon
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
2. the spanish is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the australian is between the person watching comedy movies and the game-smoker##2
4. the spanish is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Nationality    | egyptian       | australian  | spanish   |
| Movie-Genre     | comedy    | spy  | epic |
| Cigar     | siglo   | blend | game        |
| Game   | backgammon | poker     | whist      |

