3. the person traveling to new-york is between the futuristic house and the old-henry-smoker##2
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1
5. the tower house is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
