2. the person who growsdaffodil is between the malaysian and the person playing bridge##2
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the colombian##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who's sport is rugby##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
