1. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1
2. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
3. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the person watching western movies is between the owner of the lizard and the blend-smoker##2
5. the siglo-smoker is the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Cigar      | davidoff       | siglo      | blend      |
| Pet         | lizard    | goldfish | guinea-pig      |
| Movie-Genre           | adventure | western     | horror |
| Food   | papaya     | blueberry          | pumpkin       |

