2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
6. the ritmeester-smoker is the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Movie-Genre      | drama      | time-travel | comedy     |
| Hobby          | dancing   | filmmaking      | gardening     |
| Flower   | bellflower  | aconite      | daisy |
| Cigar     | bolivar | oliveros        | ritmeester     |

