.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, taxi, trike
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, turquise, grey
3 different games are played: scrabble, canasta, bridge
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, pineapple, raspberry
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the person eating pineapple is in the middle##1
4. the person eating pineapple is between the person who likes turquise and the person who likes aquamarine##2
5. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Transport      | trike     | taxi | scooter      |
| Color         | turquise  | grey       | aquamarine |
| Game   | bridge   | canasta         | scrabble     |
| Food   | pomegranate | pineapple    | raspberry     |

