.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, cranberry, grapefruit
3 different games are played: go, poker, snooker
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, traveling, hiking
City: london, new-york, hamburg
1. the person eating cranberry is the person playing snooker##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
5. the person eating cranberry is between the person playing poker and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Food      | pomegranate | cranberry      | grapefruit            |
| Game           | go | snooker | poker |
| Hobby   | traveling     | hiking        | filmmaking         |
| City   | new-york  | london    | hamburg        |

