1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the fan soul##1
2. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person who likes grey is between the fan soul and the person driving the bus##2
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the fan pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
