House: modern, art-deco, palace
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, biathlon, volleyball
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, woodworking, camping
1. the person playing go is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the palace house##2
2. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
4. the palace house is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
5. the modern house is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Game      | billiard    | go          | canasta |
| House          | palace | art-deco           | modern        |
| Sport           | biathlon | volleyball | swimming         |
| Hobby   | skydiving    | camping    | woodworking      |

