.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, february, november
City: rome, london, prague
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, fantasy, sports
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, drawing, skydiving
1. the person traveling to london is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person traveling to rome##2
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person watching sports movies is the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is the person watching fantasy movies##1
6. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Birthday   | february | january  | november     |
| City   | prague    | london | rome |
| Movie-Genre           | epic        | sports   | fantasy  |
| Hobby     | skydiving      | drawing   | baking |

