.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-18::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, cabbage, pomegranate
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, cain, dunhill
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, emerald, lilac
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, roller, skateboard
1. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person eating kale##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
5. the bolivar-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the person eating pomegranate is between the person eating kale and the person who likes emerald##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Food           | cabbage   | pomegranate   | kale |
| Cigar   | dunhill | cain   | bolivar     |
| Color   | emerald     | turquise      | lilac    |
| Transport           | snowmobile | roller | skateboard    |

