.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, banana, avocado
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, boat, car
House: colonial, palace, art-deco
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, malaysian, italian
1. the malaysian is the art-deco house##1
2. the palace house is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the colonial house is between the person eating cranberry and the person driving the skateboard##2
4. the palace house is the italian##1
5. the japanese is between the person eating banana and the palace house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Food      | cranberry | avocado     | banana        |
| Transport         | boat   | car | skateboard |
| House   | palace        | colonial       | art-deco      |
| Nationality           | italian           | japanese    | malaysian       |

