3. the futuristic house is the person playing go##1
4. the victorian house is the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person traveling to prague is between the person playing billiard and the futuristic house##2
6. the palace house is the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Flower        | poppy      | bellflower | begonia |
| City         | colone     | prague    | hannover        |
| House       | futuristic | palace   | victorian   |
| Game   | go          | canasta     | billiard       |

 